      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This example features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged power plant, delivering linear boost and high-revving engagement. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential for neutral cornering dynamics. Meticulously maintained with a refreshed vacuum system and flawless apex seals, this FD retains its factory-spec structural integrity and aesthetic purity. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering.",
